high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the dining table past the chairs.
Pick up the candle which is to the right of the empty box.
Turn around, walk past the chairs to the floor lamp to the left of the TV.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a candle by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk straight ahead. Once you pass the leather chair, turn left and walk straight ahead. Stop once you get to the middle of the wood table to your right and face the table
Pick up the small bottle with the white top to the right of the open cardboard box
Turn right to walk to the end of the table. Then turn right and walk straight ahead and walk towards the wall. When you reach the wall, turn left and walk towards the lamp
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Pick up a small bottle on a table, then turn on a lamp

high_descs: Move across the room to a long brown table behind the brown recliner chairs.
Pick up the candle that is on the table near the box.
Turn around. Carry the candle across the room to the lamp that is on the far left corner.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Carry candle to the corner so the lamp can be turned on.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the table near the windows.
Pick up the candle to the right of the box.
Turn around and veer left to the corner of the room with the lamp in it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: View a candle by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn to your right, walk forward till you get to the dining room table, turn left and face the candle.
Pick up the candle.
Turn around, then head left, then turn right when you get to the chairs, then head all the way to the back of the room, then turn left and face the lamp.
Turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: Look at a candle with the lamp on.

high_descs: Turn right, walk across the room towards the dining table, turn left in between the sofa and dining table, walk towards the middle of the table and face an open box on the table.
Pick up the candle next to the box on the table.
Turn around, turn left back towards the end of the table, turn right and walk across the room past the fireplace on the left, and turn left to face the tall lamp.
Bring the candle up next to the lamp shade and turn on the lamp shade.
anns.task_desc: Bring the candle to the lamp to turn on the lamp.
